---
title: South Indian Chicken Drumstick Curry with Garlic Butter Rice, Tomato Salad & Yoghurt
description: This slow-cooker curry boasts South Indian flavours, with curry powder and coconut milk intermingling with juicy chicken drumsticks. Time transforms these separate ingredients into a cohesive and delicious meal, served over fragrant garlic rice. It’s like a hug in a bowl!

